This is my collection of self scripted or heavily adapted tools i use.

they might be of use for you, or they don't.

Contact me for any questions.


for console use:
sshvm.expect: A tool to connect to a OpenVZ VE not reachable via ssh.
jabbermessage.py A small tool to send a jabber message to someone.

for geektools:
ip_mac.sh: A script to print all IPs (on OS/X): Ethernet, Wireless, External
downloads.py: A script to display pyload status and captchatrader.com credits
